OL,5, The father of a Michigan school gunman 
OL,6, who killed four students has been      
OL,7, convicted of manslaughter.             
OL,9,FThe trial heard that James Crumbley,   
OL,10,F47, had ignored his 15-year-old son's  
OL,11,Fmental health needs, buying him the    
OL,12,Fhandgun he used in the November 2021   
OL,13,Fattack.                                
OL,15,FThe jury deliberated for just over a   
OL,16,Fday before coming to the verdict.      
OL,18,FJennifer Crumbley, his wife, is due to 
OL,19,Fbe sentenced next month after being    
OL,20,Fconvicted on the same charges.         
